investment_objective:: The scheme will adopt a passive investment strategy. The scheme invests
in stocks comprising the Nifty 50 Index in the same proportion as in the
Index, with the objective of achieving returns equivalent to Total Returns
Index of Nifty 50 Index, by minimising the performance difference between
the benchmark index and the scheme. The Total Returns Index is an index
that reflects the returns on the index from index gain/loss plus dividend
payments by the constituent stocks. However, there is no guarantee or
assurance that the investment objective of the scheme will be achieved.
